      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's easy to say \"resilience\" but that's just words. i don't see a path back. the people i worked with, the people i cared about... they've all moved on or they're judging me. there's no \"rebuilding\" a life when the foundation is just completely rotten now. it feels like the world has already decided who i am, and it's not someone worth knowing. it's just... done. there's nothing left to salvage.",
